From 2f405f16b84935f5caf7349535bd73404dd3288a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 21:21:08 -0500
Subject: [PATCH] Route shared text through SurfaceView

Keys knock once at the pane,
AppKit composes the refrain.
Tabs keep every glyph in place,
No terminal steals a trace.
